data.description: Just outside of Creston sits this awesome semi-private 3 bedroom, 2 full bath, 2 half bath home with an awesome workshop!!  This workshop is perfect for the mechanic or hobbyist!! This dream workshop/garage is 780 Sq foot, made of 2 x 6 construction, it is fully insulated with interior plywood walls and 10' ceilings. Garage and workshop are heated with an in-floor 3 zone high efficiency natural gas hydronic heating system, 8 ft 8 inch clearance x 18 foot wide garage door with remotes, an interior garage door separates the workshop area which has custom work bench areas, window air conditioning, frig, microwave, and sink with water. The 2 ton capacity chain hoist is included!! Garage and workshop have multiple compressed air fittings connected to a large compressor which is stored in the additional lawn care shed behind the garage.  Home amenities include new appliances and beautiful countertops with a nice big island in the kitchen. The great room is 841 sq feet with a stone-faced gas fireplace, subfloor hydronic heating, and patio doors overlooking the .75 acre yard which includes mature trees, a lily pond, and the firepit corral.  Enjoy those sunrises with unobstructed easterly views!! The Great Room has plenty of space for the entire family or perfect for entertaining guests.  The Master bedroom en-suite on the 2nd level boasts patio doors to your own private balcony, a very large master bathroom, and a custom walk-in closet. Perfect views from this room!  The main floor full bath has a very nice tiled walk-in shower with an additional custom walk-in closet and laundry area. The bonus room on the main level would be an excellent gaming room/ playroom for the kids or an additional bedroom with a bit of creativity.  Home is 2 x 6 constructed with tight insulation, plus 200 amp underground electrical service. Concrete patio surrounds the entire home. Home has a leaf guard gutter system, the furnace and tankless water heater are in great condition. Roof is approximately 10 years old.  So many upgrades have been completed during this seller's ownership. This home has been superbly maintained. Come take a look!!
